Young girls engaging in online dating have been urged to always exercise due diligence following the disappearance of a beautiful girl based in Jos, Plateau State who went to visit a man she met on Facebook. It was gathered that the girl has been missing for five days now. The girl named Sadiya has lost contact with family members and her mobile phone has been switched off. Efforts are being made on social media to create awareness about her missing status and find her. See the post crying for help: Source